data.description: Nestled in the highly sought-after Minisink Valley School District, this well maintained contemporary bilevel sits on a sprawling 1.8-acre parcel adorned with mature trees and lush shrubbery - a beautiful backdrop to countless cherished memories made on this remarkable property throughout the years. Now it's your turn to create lasting memories here and a story of your very own.    As you step inside to the main floor, natural light floods the airy living room, showcasing a charming shiplap woodburning fireplace and ornamental lighting accentuated by vaulted ceilings. An open floor plan seamlessly transitions into the formal dining room, offering slider access to the rear deck overlooking the picturesque yard. The heart of this home lies in the recently updated spacious kitchen, a culinary enthusiast's dream! Revel in an abundance of cabinetry and quartz countertops, complete with adjustable stainless steel sliding pull-outs, modern stainless steel appliances, and a generously sized center island accented with decorative pendant lighting. This island also features a built-in wine rack and countertop seating, making it the perfect space for meal prep and entertaining guests.  Down the hall, you'll discover three generously sized bedrooms and two full baths, including a primary suite with its own private full bath and a decently sized walk-in closet, maximizing your storage options.  On the lower level, a sliding barn door conceals the private laundry room with built-in clothing rack and cabinetry. On this floor you will also discover a cozy family room, a spacious fourth bedroom (currently being used as a home office), and another full bath. This level offers direct access to the two-car attached garage that can easily accommodate large SUVs and still leave room for additional storage.  For added comfort and convenience, this home features a 2-zone heating system and an energy-efficient central air system. Located within walking distance to the quaint village of Otisville, you'll have access to various dining options, post office, places of worship, the Metro North train station, and the beautifully maintained Veteran Memorial Park.  Don't miss this opportunity to make this incredible property your forever home. Schedule a viewing today and begin creating your own lifetime of cherished memories here tomorrow!
